                        Clark
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1949v09</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d1308</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">1308</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1949-07-22T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1949-07-22T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-07-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-07-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="1308" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1308">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.1115/7–2249: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister-Counselor of Embassy in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clark</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Canton</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-07-22">July 22,
                            1949</date>.<lb/>[Received July 22—4:11 a. m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cantel 799. Foreign Office volunteers it has no objection should Americans desire
                    depart Shanghai on <hi rend="italic">Anchises</hi>, safe conduct for which has
                    been given.</p>
                <p>Sent Shanghai 449; repeated Department Cantel 799, Nanking 531.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Clark</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
